{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sandustry is a mining and automation game with pixel-based physics.\u00a0The Demo version showcases the first few processing tiers on a limited map.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Falling sand</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Everything in the game is part of a falling sand style simulation and it's up to you to curb the chaos.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Automation</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Create an automated factory with increasingly intricate processing lines.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Mining</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use various tools and weapons to mine and dig deeper and deeper for sand and raw materials.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Base-building</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Setup your base and build a logistics network for transporting and refining sand.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Exploration</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore and discover temples and structures from an ancient civilization.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solve puzzles to acquire key items.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Upgrades and tech</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock new refining methods and tech such as drones, new buildings and multistep processing. Upgrade your weapons and equipment.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490390/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738766360","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490390/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738766360","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490390/9379727bada16cb3f2dcf72a7d43b3b64390f37f/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738766360","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490390/9379727bada16cb3f2dcf72a7d43b3b64390f37f/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738766360","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description